The success of a product farm company is completed determined by whatever zeitgeist there may be surrounding a certain company and their ability to market their product effectively. As for the product itself, its quality will be represented in any product farm companys stock performance, as noted above when both companies took a dip in the beginning of 2022 that they are still climbing back from. This is likely due to inflation.
